  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/921a1ebb2132202c8c0704d885e14bc7.poster.avif?t=1739349833\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/921a1ebb2132202c8c0704d885e14bc7.webm?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/921a1ebb2132202c8c0704d885e14bc7.mp4?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deathless: Survivors</strong> is an online cooperative game in the Survival Roguelite genre. Enjoyed Vampire Survivors? Play it in 3D, with friends! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a dark, engulfing world where you and your friends must battle hordes of enemies, attacking in waves every minute. Your survival depends on combining devastating spells, tactically using powerful weapons, and making quick decisions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BRUTAL MULTIPLAYER COMBAT</strong>: Play with your friends to defeat hordes of enemies. Teamwork will be necessary to beat the toughest bosses</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/f2ea0d50a42d1885ebcf729b5420445b.poster.avif?t=1739349833\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/f2ea0d50a42d1885ebcf729b5420445b.webm?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/f2ea0d50a42d1885ebcf729b5420445b.mp4?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VAST PLAYER PROGRESSION AND BUILD CHOICES</strong>: Hundreds of different builds with unique heroes and skill combinations, each leading to special ultimate abilities</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/91100047a0ff9309e505d21e5910b6e7.poster.avif?t=1739349833\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/91100047a0ff9309e505d21e5910b6e7.webm?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/91100047a0ff9309e505d21e5910b6e7.mp4?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FOLLOW THE STORY</strong>: Unique storyline with beautifully crafted 3D characters. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/ce35ef7e7b8cdf5e70861fc25086232c.poster.avif?t=1739349833\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/ce35ef7e7b8cdf5e70861fc25086232c.webm?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/ce35ef7e7b8cdf5e70861fc25086232c.mp4?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/921a1ebb2132202c8c0704d885e14bc7.poster.avif?t=1739349833\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/921a1ebb2132202c8c0704d885e14bc7.webm?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/921a1ebb2132202c8c0704d885e14bc7.mp4?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deathless: Survivors</strong> is an online cooperative game in the Survival Roguelite genre. Enjoyed Vampire Survivors? Play it in 3D, with friends! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a dark, engulfing world where you and your friends must battle hordes of enemies, attacking in waves every minute. Your survival depends on combining devastating spells, tactically using powerful weapons, and making quick decisions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BRUTAL MULTIPLAYER COMBAT</strong>: Play with your friends to defeat hordes of enemies. Teamwork will be necessary to beat the toughest bosses</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/f2ea0d50a42d1885ebcf729b5420445b.poster.avif?t=1739349833\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/f2ea0d50a42d1885ebcf729b5420445b.webm?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/f2ea0d50a42d1885ebcf729b5420445b.mp4?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VAST PLAYER PROGRESSION AND BUILD CHOICES</strong>: Hundreds of different builds with unique heroes and skill combinations, each leading to special ultimate abilities</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/91100047a0ff9309e505d21e5910b6e7.poster.avif?t=1739349833\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/91100047a0ff9309e505d21e5910b6e7.webm?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/91100047a0ff9309e505d21e5910b6e7.mp4?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FOLLOW THE STORY</strong>: Unique storyline with beautifully crafted 3D characters. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/ce35ef7e7b8cdf5e70861fc25086232c.poster.avif?t=1739349833\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/ce35ef7e7b8cdf5e70861fc25086232c.webm?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443090/extras/ce35ef7e7b8cdf5e70861fc25086232c.mp4?t=1739349833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
